# Ropar Institute Portal

Ropar Institute Portal is an all-in-one campus super app designed to simplify academic life, campus services, and student collaboration at IIT Ropar. It aims to centralize essential student utilities into a single, efficient, and user-friendly digital platform.

---

## Acknowledgement

We sincerely thank the IIT Ropar faculty and hackathon organizers for providing us with the opportunity, guidance, and platform to develop this project. This initiative has helped us strengthen our technical, collaborative, and problem-solving skills while working on real-world campus challenges.

We welcome feedback and suggestions to further improve the Ropar Institute Portal.

---

## Installation

1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies
3. Configure environment variables
4. Run the server
5. Open in browser

## Main Features

Academics
Live timetable with real-time updates
LMS Lite for assignments, grades, and submissions
Attendance tracking and prediction
GPA calculator and exam reminders
Smart study planning tools

Mess and Food
Live mess menu with ratings
Food waste tracking and donation support

Communication
Smart mail summarizer
Important notices and deadline alerts

Marketplace and Exchange
Lost and found system
Buy and sell marketplace
Skill portfolio and mini freelancing hub

Hostel and Services
Roommate matching system
Complaint and maintenance tracking
Laundry and utility alerts

Travel and Navigation
Cab pooling and travel sharing
Nearby places discovery
Smart campus maps

Community
Clubs, forums, and group chats
Events and crowd prediction
Polls and engagement features

Safety and Security
Emergency SOS and safe walk
Anonymous reporting system

Smart Tools
Event crowd estimation
Equipment booking system
Basic recommendation system

---

## Project Objectives

To improve student productivity and engagement
To reduce administrative delays
To enhance transparency in campus services
To promote collaboration and sustainability
To provide a scalable digital campus solution

---

## Technology Overview

Frontend: Web and mobile responsive interface
Backend: REST API-based modular architecture
Database: Secure and optimized data storage
Authentication: Role-based access system
Hosting: Cloud-ready infrastructure

